This is what your scalp’s been waiting for... trust us.

Launched today, our NEW Scalp Soothing Treatment instantly calms irritation, tackles flakes, and boosts scalp health from the very first use.

Powered by Dandrilys®, Vitamin E & Coconut Oil, and with a built-in massager to exfoliate, hydrate and restore balance, this multi-tasking treatment also works to leave locks nourished and lustrous. 

Pair with our I’m No Flake Scalp Soothing Shampoo, and say goodbye to flakes, dryness and itch, and hello to healthy, happy hair 💆‍♀️

From tousled, sea sprayed locks to designer staples, this dreamy prize is giving luxury meets effortless. It even features our NEW Sea Salt Spray, the secret to creating beachy waves with serious staying power 🌊

Here’s what you’ll win:
👜Marc Jacobs beach bag

latestPosts.caption:
Effortless, not overdone. A unisex essential made for all hair types and all plans.

Starting with our Wonder Balm to prep, then the NEW Sea Salt Spray to enhance natural texture, this two-step routine creates relaxed, wave-led styling without heat or fuss.

The Sea Salt Spray formula delivers body and texture without the crunch, using blue sea kale and sea fennel to keep hair hydrated while achieving a tousled, undone finish. The result? Textured, tousled and effortlessly undone.

@theoching_
⠀
Shop now on Amazon

Discover the secret to effortless texture with our new Session Styling Sea Salt Spray🌊

In this exclusive interview, Our Founder @paulpercivalhair shares what sets this formula apart. From sustainably sourced Dorset sea salt to a non crunchy finish that delivers soft, beachy texture for all hair types.

Spritz into damp hair and air dry for a naturally tousled look, or diffuse for added definition. A unisex essential for modern, lived in styling.

#beachhair #percyandreed

Meet your blow-dry’s new essential: Wonder Balm Hair Primer - 72 hours of frizz + humidity protection, with that healthy, glossy finish you love ✨
